title: 20th Century Boy And Girl
description: The friendship and love lives of three single virgins born in 1983. The boy they liked in their youth shows up one day when they live in rundown apartments. They discover the meaning of home, family and friendship

items.description: Sa Jin Jin is a celebrity in her 30s. She is currently the most popular star, and everyone is head-over-heels for her. Despite her popularity, Jin Jin is only in love with a man named Anthony. Jin Jin decides to do the variety show in Hong Kong. Gong Ji Won is living in Hong Kong while working at a hedge fund. Meanwhile, a shocking news article has spread virally.
items.title: 20th Century Boy And Girl EP 1

items.description: A sex tape is released, claiming that the woman in the video is Jin Jin. Jin Jin visits her friend at the OBGYN who recently underwent surgery. A rumor starts to spread that she is pregnant. The word is out about Jin Jin staying at an OBGYN for seven hours and leaving in the middle of the night. Reporters try to hunt her down to obtain more information.
items.title: 20th Century Boy And Girl EP 2

items.description: Jin Jin and Ah Reum keep looking up information on Gong Ji Won on the internet, and they find out that he is married. Ah Reum wants to ask Dong Hoon out, but she hesitates to make the first move. Anthony hears that there could be a reunion show for boys be ambitious and visits Terius to talk about it. However, Terius doesn't seem too interested by the idea.
items.title: 20th Century Boy And Girl EP 3

items.description: Ji Won runs into Jin Jin late at night at a theater. He asks Jin Jin to have a quick meal at a street stall, but she refuses. Meanwhile, Ah Reum witnesses Dong Hoon kissing Ji Hye after a get-together and gets her heart broken. Ji Won goes home after a long time and meets Anthony, his step-brother.
items.title: 20th Century Boy And Girl EP 4

items.description: Jin Jin runs into Ji Won who's temporarily staying at Jin Jin's parent's place. She learns that Ji Won's not married. Meanwhile, Jin Jin starts shooting 'We Got Married' with Anthony, but they have to keep it a secret. Jin Jin and Anthony meet again for the second shoot of 'We Got Married'. They have to invite their friends and family for the wedding.
items.title: 20th Century Boy And Girl EP 5

items.description: As part of a wedding event, Jin Jin has to pick Anthony among three men, including Ji Won, who are hidden behind masks. Jin Jin mistakenly picks Ji Won, so Anthony feels disappointed. Meanwhile, Anthony loses the wedding ring he exchanged with Jin Jin. Jin Jin meets Anthony at a restaurant and has dinner with him. Jin Jin gets nervous as she thinks of it as a date.
items.title: 20th Century Boy And Girl EP 6

items.description: Jin Jin and Ji Won become honest with each other. Gradually, they start to bond more. Meanwhile, during the gathering of Anthony and Jin Jin's variety show, Jin Jin becomes a black knight for him. During the gathering, Jin Jin is determined to protect Anthony. She sits next to him and secretly switches his drinks with her water. Consequently, she gets very drunk.
items.title: 20th Century Boy And Girl EP 7

items.description: Jin Jin, Ji Won, and Anthony have dinner together. Anthony becomes curious about how Ji Won feels about Jin Jin. Meanwhile, Jin Jin suddenly collapses and is taken to the hospital. Anthony presents Jin Jin with a small tree for their dinner. Jin Jin tells him that it's an amazing gift. Anthony wants to tell her that it's actually from Ji Won, but Ji Won stops him from saying anything.
items.title: 20th Century Boy And Girl EP 8

items.description: Thanks to Anthony, Jin Jin's life is saved. After waking up and finding out that Ji Won has not called her once, she becomes sad. When she finds out that he has returned home, her sadness deepens. In the end, she decides to tell him exactly how she feels. A commercial offer related to rubber gloves and newlyweds come in, but Anthony is hesitant to accept it.
items.title: 20th Century Boy And Girl EP 9

items.description: While filming 'We Got Married' on Jeju Island, Jin Jin and Anthony become closer. Meanwhile, Ji Won cancels the blind date and reevaluates his feelings for Jin Jin. He makes a decision. After shooting 'We Got Married', the entire crew eats dinner. Jin Jin accidentally eats shrimp and gets an allergic reaction.
items.title: 20th Century Boy And Girl EP 10

items.description: Jin Jin and Ji Won start dating in secret and enjoy their time together. Meanwhile, Ji Won decides to disclose to Anthony about his relationship with Jin Jin. However, things do not go their way. Ah Reum and Young Shim notice that Ji Won and Jin Jin like each other. However, the latter two do not realize this. Meanwhile, rumors spread about how Jin Jin and Anthony might get married.
items.title: 20th Century Boy And Girl EP 11

items.description: Ji Won tries numerous times to tell his brother, Anthony, about his relationship with Jin Jin. However, every time he attempts to do so, something gets in the way. Anthony, however, notices their relationship and is in a dilemma. Ah Reum and Woo Sung go on their first date, but it becomes too awkward. Jin Jin's mother has a hard time seeing.
items.title: 20th Century Boy And Girl EP 12

items.description: Ji Won tells his brother, Anthony, that Jin Jin is his first love as well as his girl-friend. Meanwhile, Jin Jin is in shock after finding out about her mother's glaucoma. Depressed and desperate, she heads out with Ji Won to find her older sister, Ho Sung. Both Anthony and Ji Won strive to look for Jin Jin's sister.
items.title: 20th Century Boy And Girl EP 13

items.description: After much hardship, Jin Jin and Ji Won successfully find Jin Jin's sister, Ho Sung. Jin Jin begs her to go back home with her, but Ho Sung is determined not to go. Meanwhile, Mi Kyung decides to get surgery for her glaucoma, and the family is nervous.
items.title: 20th Century Boy And Girl EP 14

items.description: Jin Jin meets Anthony on a new drama, and they practice together. Meanwhile, Ji Won's ex, Bella, contacts him after a long time and gives him mixed emotions. Jin Jin becomes anxious. Jin Jin and Ji Won go on a double date with Jin Jin's stylist, Mi Dal and Ji Won's secretary. Meanwhile, Ah Reum meets Woo Sung's sisters. The sisters all thank her for dating their ugly brother.
items.title: 20th Century Boy And Girl EP 15

items.description: Jin Jin embraces Ji Won's hurt past. Seeing this, Ji Won makes a big decision and proposes to her. However, articles involving paparazzi shots of Jin Jin arise. Jin Jin and Ji Won almost get caught by her brother. Jin Jin's dad senses something going on between her and Ji Won.
items.title: 20th Century Boy And Girl EP 16

description: Seo Yeon hates handsome guys the most in the world. One day, she bumps into Kang Woo, 'a young, handsome, and rich boy.' But they once got involved in an unpleasant situation before?
title: Love With Flaws

items.description: Seo Yeon hates handsome guys the most in the world. One day, she bumps into Kang Woo, 'a young, handsome, and rich boy.' But they once got involved in an unpleasant situation before?
items.title: Love With Flaws EP 1

items.description: Kang Woo realizes the cause of his chronic diarrhea is Seo Yeon. He asks her out of the blue. How will Seo Yeon respond to the random confession?
items.title: Love With Flaws EP 2

items.description: Kang Woo wants to pick on Seo Yeon, but he can't somehow stop thinking about her. Seo Yeon is in trouble because she is a temporary worker, and someone sniffs around her.
items.title: Love With Flaws EP 3

items.description: Seo Yeon and Kang Woo think about the time they were together, but they both have changed too much. Kang Woo feels confused about his feelings for Seo Yeon, and Seo Yeon visits him at his house.
items.title: Love With Flaws EP 4

items.description: Kang Woo admits that he's into Seo Yeon. He asks her out once again with a fancy surprise, but Seo Yeon has a big misunderstanding about him.
items.title: Love With Flaws EP 5

items.description: Seo Yeon pretends to be the girlfriend for Kang Woo but gets infuriated after finding out the truth. Kang Woo is disappointed and makes up his mind.
items.title: Love With Flaws EP 6

items.description: Min Hyuk aggressively expresses how he feels for Seo Yeon. Kang Woo, feeling anxious, decides to ask Seo Yeon out once again.
items.title: Love With Flaws EP 7

items.description: Seo Yeon realizes that Kang Woo wasn't lying. Although she politely rejects him, she can't stop thinking about him, unlike the other time.
items.title: Love With Flaws EP 8

items.description: After having the first kiss, Kang Woo expects to start a serious relationship with Seo Yeon, but Seo Yeon hesitates. And she tells what she really has on her mind after several times of sighing.
items.title: Love With Flaws EP 9

items.description: Kang Woo is fired from the chairman position for overusing his power, and Min Hyuk becomes the new chairman. As Seo Yeon regains her lost memory, she remembers the reason for her parents' death.
items.title: Love With Flaws EP 10

items.description: After regaining all of her lost memory, Seo Yeon avoids Kang Woo's calls. They start to fall out with each other again, and Seo Yeon decides to leave Kang Woo.
items.title: Love With Flaws EP 11

items.description: Not to break up with Seo Yeon, Kang Woo tries not to run into Seo Yeon. But Seo Yeon harshly breaks up with Kang Woo and shed tears.
items.title: Love With Flaws EP 12

items.description: Kang Woo learns the real reason that Seo Yeon avoids him and feels tormented. Seo Yeong gets a phone call from Kang Woo and is shocked to hear about the accident.
items.title: Love With Flaws EP 13

items.description: Although Kang Woo and Seo Yeon learn how they feel for each other, Kang Woo blames himself and thinks he should be abandoned. So he decides not to be with Seo Yeon. What will happen to the two?
items.title: Love With Flaws EP 14

items.description: Kang Woo and Seo Yeon are back at home but feel awkward, not knowing what to do. They try to break the ice, but someone else is watching them there.
items.title: Love With Flaws EP 15

items.description: Everything seems to go smoothly, but Kang Woo keeps hiding something from Seo Yeon. What is he hiding?
items.title: Love With Flaws EP 16
